---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me - Ali Mansoor">
  <main>
    <h2 class="animate-fade-in">About Me</h2>
    <p class="animate-slide-up">
      I'm a Software Engineer passionate about building exceptional user experiences across mobile and web platforms. My professional journey began during my final year at FAST-NUCES, where I transitioned from academic learning into real-world software development. My career has been characterized by continuous growth, diverse technical exposure, and an unwavering commitment to engineering excellence.
    </p>

    <p class="animate-slide-up-delay">
      <strong className="company-highlight">Grade Up (Pvt.) Ltd — August 2023 to August 2024</strong><br/>
      I began my professional career as a Junior Flutter Developer at Grade Up, a pivotal role that shaped my foundation in mobile development. During this period, I transitioned from purely academic knowledge to practical software engineering, working on real-world Flutter applications. This position exposed me to fundamental web technologies and the MERN stack, helping me understand the broader landscape of full-stack development. I focused on hands-on application development, implementing features while learning modern frameworks and development methodologies. This experience significantly enhanced my problem-solving capabilities, taught me the importance of clean code and scalability, and equipped me with practical skills to contribute meaningfully to professional development teams.
    </p>

    <p class="animate-slide-up-delay">
      <strong className="company-highlight">Paymo — July 2024 to September 2025</strong><br/>
      My transition to Paymo marked a significant evolution in my career. I progressed from intern to full-time Flutter Developer, contributing to one of Pakistan's leading fintech platforms serving millions of users. At Paymo, I was responsible for delivering mission-critical features including sophisticated QR code scanning systems for seamless payment transactions, real-time payment tracking providing users with instant transaction visibility, and secure money transfer infrastructure handling complex financial operations. I designed responsive UI components that improved app usability by 40%, architected scalable application structures that reduced payment processing time by 35%, and collaborated cross-functionally to ensure seamless integration across Android and iOS platforms. This experience deepened my expertise in financial application development, performance optimization, and working within agile, fast-paced environments handling high-stakes features.
    </p>

    <p class="animate-slide-up-delay">
      <strong className="company-highlight">The Essential Studio — June 2024 to May 2025 (Concurrent)</strong><br/>
      While progressing at Paymo, I took on the role of Development Consultant at The Essential Studio, a creative technology firm. In this capacity, I provided comprehensive software consultation and technical planning for 10+ client projects spanning diverse domains. I collaborated with cross-functional teams to deliver scalable product strategies, designed resilient software systems to meet complex client requirements, and streamlined remote development workflows improving team productivity by 30%. This consulting experience broadened my perspective on diverse technology stacks, client management, and architectural decision-making at scale.
    </p>

    <p class="animate-slide-up-delay">
      <strong className="company-highlight">Beyond One — October 2025 to Present</strong><br/>
      Currently, I serve as a Flutter Developer at Beyond One, where I contribute to Virgin Connect Roam, an innovative international eSIM roaming platform operating across multiple countries. In this role, I develop and optimize complex Flutter features for global users, enhance UI/UX flows to accommodate diverse user demographics and languages, and ensure seamless connectivity across international networks. This position has expanded my understanding of global application architecture, multi-region deployment strategies, and building user experiences that transcend geographical and cultural boundaries.
    </p>

    <p class="animate-slide-up-delay">
      Throughout my career progression, I have consistently demonstrated the ability to adapt to diverse technical challenges, collaborate effectively within dynamic teams, and deliver production-grade solutions that drive business impact. My expertise spans Flutter for mobile development, React and Next.js for web development, state management, RESTful API integration, and scalable application architecture. I am committed to continuous learning, exploring emerging technologies, contributing to open-source projects, and maintaining the highest standards of code quality and user experience design.
    </p>

    <p class="animate-slide-up-delay">
      Outside of professional development, I maintain a balanced lifestyle through sports and recreational activities, including football, competitive gaming, table tennis, and fitness training—pursuits that reinforce my commitment to discipline, resilience, and continuous improvement.
    </p>

    <div class="skills-section">
      <h3 class="animate-fade-in">Technical Skills</h3>
      <div class="skills-grid animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #007AFF;">Flutter</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #61DAFB;">React</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #000000;">Next.js</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #3178C6;">TypeScript</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #F1DB4D;">JavaScript</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #06B6D4;">Tailwind CSS</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #764ABC;">Redux</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #F16529;">REST APIs</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #00D9FF;">Dart</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #47A248;">Git</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #13C3E7;">State Management</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #FF6B6B;">Responsive Design</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: var(--color);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  p {
    max-width: 90ch;
    color: var(--color);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  p a {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-slide-up {
    animation: slideUp 1s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  .animate-slide-up-delay {
    animation: slideUp 1s ease-out 0.4s both;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  @keyframes slideUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .skills-section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .skills-section h3 {
    color: var(--color);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .career-title {
    color: var(--color);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .career-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border-radius: 0.8rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .career-section:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    transform: translateX(10px);
  }

  .career-section h4 {
    color: var(--color);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .career-section p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .career-section strong {
    color: var(--color);
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .skills-grid.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .skill-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    background: rgba(var(--primary-rgb, 52, 81, 178), 0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--skill-color, var(--primary));
    color: var(--skill-color, var(--primary));
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .skill-pill:hover {
    background: var(--skill-color, var(--primary));
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(var(--skill-color, 52, 81, 178, 0.3));
  }

  @media (max-width: 450px) {
    p {
      font-size: small;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .skills-section h3 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
    .skill-pill {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
